title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - ATR 42-600/72-600 - Using the checklist inside the aircraft
description:
In this video we will look at how you can use the checklists inside the ATR 42-600/72-600. Normally you would use the checklist which can be found by using the menu bar on the top. However this aircraft also has the checklists integrated in the center display of the aircraft. In this video we will look where to find them, which ones are available and how to use them.
